dcms_media/image/dropdown-workplace-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"278\" height=\"161\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"__title\">教育制度・資格取得</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"dropdown__item\"><a href=\"/recruit/workplace/welfare_system/\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"__thum\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/dropdown-workplace-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"278\" height=\"161\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"__title\">福利厚生・社内制度等</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/guideline/\">募集要項</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n<ul class=\"header__link\">\r\n<li class=\"__icon-building\"><a href=\"/\">コーポレートサイトへ</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"__icon-people\"><a href=\"/recruit/guideline/#entry\">エントリーはこちら</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"header__menu js-menu-trigger\"><span class=\"ee\"> <!--ee--> </span> <span class=\"ee\"> <!--ee--> </span> <span class=\"ee\"> <!--ee--> </span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"js-overlay\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"bs_header-spacer\"> </div>\n\r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        <!-- ブロック貼り付けエリア -->\r\n        <div id=\"dcms_layoutPageBlockPasteArea\">\r\n            <!-- ブロック -->\r\n            <div id=\"dcms_layoutPageBlock\">\r\n                <section class=\"p-r-main\">\n<div class=\"container my-0\">\n<div class=\"p-r-main-inner\">\n<p class=\"mb-0\"><span class=\"-lead-en\">Let’s have a fun！</span></p>\n<h1 class=\"mb-0 -lead\">”楽しく働く”がここにある</h1>\n<p class=\"-sup\">あなたの才能で未来を創造する。イノベーションを生み出すITコンサルティングファーム。</p>\n<div class=\"row mt-4 mt-xl-5\">\n<div class=\"col-12 col-md-6\">\n<div class=\"btn btn-accent-01 p-icon-arr btn-block\"><a href=\"/recruit/guideline/#entry\">エントリーはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"p-r-news\">\n<div class=\"container my-0\">\n<div class=\"p-r-news-inner\">\n<div class=\"swiper-news\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\"><div class=\"swiper-slide\"><dl>\n<dt class=\"rss_date\">2026/05/01</dt>\n<dd class=\"rss_title\"><a href=\"https://www.sr-co.co.jp/news/20260531/\"><span class=\"rss_new\">NEW</span> 5月31日(日)　インターンシップ＆キャリア発見フェア（神戸）参加のお知らせ</a></dd>\n<dd class=\"rss_contents\"></dd>\n</dl></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><dl>\n<dt class=\"rss_date\">2026/04/13</dt>\n<dd class=\"rss_title\"><a href=\"https://www.sr-co.co.jp/news/20260524/\">5月24日(日)　インターンシップ＆キャリア発見フェア（京都）参加のお知らせ</a></dd>\n<dd class=\"rss_contents\"></dd>\n</dl></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><dl>\n<dt class=\"rss_date\">2026/02/20</dt>\n<dd class=\"rss_title\"><a href=\"https://www.sr-co.co.jp/news/20260313/\">3月13日(金)　「たじま合同企業説明会」参加のお知らせ</a></dd>\n<dd class=\"rss_contents\"></dd>\n</dl></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-swiper-navi\">\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev\"><!--button--></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next\"><!--button--></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"p-r-about\">\n<div class=\"container mb-5 mb-md-6 mb-lg-8 mt-md-5 mt-lg-6\">\n<div class=\"p-r-about-inner\">\n<div class=\"-img rounded-20\"><img class=\"d-none d-md-block\" src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-aboutus.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"544\" /> <img class=\"d-block d-md-none\" src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-aboutus-sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"360\" /></div>\n<div class=\"-txt\">\n<p class=\"p-r-title-en font-weight-bold text-main\">About Us</p>\n<h2 class=\"h4 font-weight-bold mt-md-3 mt-lg-4 mb-0\">システムリサーチを知る</h2>\n<p class=\"mt-4 mt-xl-5 text-left\">システムリサーチはITサービスソリューションを活用してお客様の課題（困りごと）を解決する会社です。</p>\n<div class=\"row mt-4 mt-xl-5\">\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-11\">\n<div class=\"btn btn-white p-icon-arr btn-block\"><a href=\"/recruit/about/\">詳しくはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mt-5 mt-md-7 mt-lg-8\">\n<div class=\"container my-0 text-center\">\n<p class=\"p-r-title-en font-weight-bold text-main\">Works</p>\n<h2 class=\"h4 font-weight-bold mt-md-3 mt-lg-4 mb-0\">仕事を知る</h2>\n<p class=\"mt-4 mt-md-5\">学校や自治体、医療機関、介護施設、民間企業といった分野に、<br class=\"d-none d-md-block d-lg-none\" />さまざまなITサービスソリューションを提供しています。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-r-works mt-4 mt-lg-5\"><a class=\"-item\" href=\"/recruit/job/#link-1\">\n<div class=\"-item-inner\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-works-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"666\" height=\"400\" />\n<p class=\"-txt h4 text-white\">営業</p>\n</div>\n</a> <a class=\"-item\" href=\"/recruit/job/#link-2\">\n<div class=\"-item-inner\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-works-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"666\" height=\"400\" />\n<p class=\"-txt h4 text-white\">システムエンジニア</p>\n</div>\n</a> <a class=\"-item\" href=\"/recruit/job/#link-3\">\n<div class=\"-item-inner\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-works-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"666\" height=\"400\" />\n<p class=\"-txt h4 text-white\">事務</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"container mb-0 mt-4 mt-md-5\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"btn btn-white p-icon-arr btn-block\"><a href=\"/recruit/job/\">詳しくはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mt-6 mt-md-7 mt-md-8\">\n<div class=\"container my-0\">\n<div class=\"p-r-break\">\n<div class=\"-txt\">\n<p class=\"p-r-title-en font-weight-bold text-main\">Project Story</p>\n<h2 class=\"h4 font-weight-bold mt-md-4 mb-0\">プロジェクトストーリー</h2>\n<div class=\"img-fluid d-block d-md-none rounded-20\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-story-sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"300\" /></div>\n<p class=\"mt-4 mt-lg-5 text-left\">プロジェクトには職種の異なる様々な人がかかわっています。<br />全体を統括するマネージャー、最前線に立つ営業、スキルを駆使し要望をカタチにしていくSE、チーム全員でプロジェクトの完遂を目指します。</p>\n<div class=\"row mt-4 mt-lg-5\">\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"btn btn-white p-icon-arr btn-block\"><a href=\"/recruit/job/projectstory/\">詳しくはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"-img ml-auto d-none d-md-block\">\n<div class=\"img-fluid rounded-20\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-story.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"603\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"p-r-person mt-5 mt-md-6 mt-lg-7 py-5  py-md-6 py-lg-7\">\n<div class=\"p-r-person-inner text-center\">\n<div class=\"container my-0 text-white\">\n<p class=\"p-r-title-en font-weight-bold\">Person</p>\n<h2 class=\"h4 font-weight-bold mt-md-3 mt-lg-4 mb-0\">人を知る</h2>\n<p class=\"mt-4 mt-md-5\">&nbsp;<span>現場の最前線で働いている当社の社員をご紹介します。</span><br /><br /></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper mt-5\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><a href=\"/recruit/staff/staff-9/\">\n<div class=\"rounded-10 img-fluid\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-person-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"625\" /></div>\n<div class=\"p-txt text-white bg-accent-01-op p-3 text-left\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 font-weight-bold mb-1\">営業職（公共・医療担当）</h3>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">2012年 中途入社</p>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">文系　文学部 卒</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><a href=\"/recruit/staff/staff-18/\">\n<div class=\"rounded-10 img-fluid\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-person-18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"625\" /></div>\n<div class=\"p-txt text-white bg-accent-01-op p-3 text-left\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 font-weight-bold mb-1\">システムエンジニア（介護・福祉担当）</h3>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">2023年 新卒入社</p>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">文系　商学部 卒</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><a href=\"/recruit/staff/staff-6/\">\n<div class=\"rounded-10 img-fluid\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/top-person-10.png\" alt=\"top-person-10.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1251\" /></div>\n<div class=\"p-txt text-white bg-accent-01-op p-3 text-left\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 font-weight-bold mb-1\">システムエンジニア（ＮＷ担当）</h3>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">2022年 新卒入社</p>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">文系　人文学部 卒</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><a href=\"/recruit/staff/staff-8/\">\n<div class=\"rounded-10 img-fluid\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-person-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"625\" /></div>\n<div class=\"p-txt text-white bg-accent-01-op p-3 text-left\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 font-weight-bold mb-1\">システムエンジニア（介護・福祉担当）</h3>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">2018年 新卒入社</p>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">理系　IT系専門学校 卒</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><a href=\"/recruit/staff/staff-16/\">\n<div class=\"rounded-10 img-fluid\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/top-person-15.png\" alt=\"top-person-10.png\" width=\"1002\" height=\"1251\" /></div>\n<div class=\"p-txt text-white bg-accent-01-op p-3 text-left\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 font-weight-bold mb-1\">システムエンジニア（医療担当）</h3>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">2010年 中途入社</p>\n<p class=\"mb-0 small\">理系　電子工学科 卒</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-swiper-navi\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container my-0\">\n<div class=\"row mt-5 mt-lg-5\">\n<div class=\"col-11 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"btn btn-white p-icon-arr btn-block\"><a href=\"/recruit/staff/\">詳しくはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mt-5 mt-md-7 mb-4 mb-md-3\">\n<div class=\"container my-0\">\n<div class=\"p-r-break\">\n<div class=\"-txt order-1 order-md-2 ml-auto\">\n<p class=\"p-r-title-en font-weight-bold text-main\">Company</p>\n<h2 class=\"h4 font-weight-bold mt-md-4 mb-0\">職場を知る</h2>\n<div class=\"img-fluid d-block d-md-none rounded-20\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-company-sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"300\" /></div>\n<p class=\"mt-4 mt-lg-5 text-left\">システムリサーチは、社員が健康でやる気に満ちあふれた働きやすい職場を目指しています。<br />「社員の成長の総和が企業の成長につながる」という考えのもと、社員の成長を支援し、知識やスキルの習得を促進しています。</p>\n<div class=\"row mt-4 mt-lg-5\">\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"btn btn-white p-icon-arr btn-block\"><a href=\"/recruit/workplace/\">詳しくはこちら</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"-img order-2 order-md-1 d-none d-md-block\">\n<div class=\"img-fluid rounded-20\"><img src=\"/dcms_media/image/recruit-top-company.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"603\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\r\n          